    <b>Shadowbane Beta Phase 1 winding down.</b><br>
    <font size=1><b>Date:</b> Thursday, March 29 @ 22:12:23 EST<br><b>Topic:</b> Beta Test News<br><br>
    </center><font size=2>
    Warden posted <a href="http://shadowbane.godgames.com/cgi-bin/wwwthreads/showthreaded.pl?Cat=&Board=discussion&Number=22357">this</a> today, saying that Phase 1 was ending.  His exact words:<br>
<blockquote>
Hey gang, 

Just a quick heads up, we're starting to wrap up Phase 1, so we may skip the update for next week. I'll see if there is anything we can release, but I'd rather give you warning now so that you don't get too hyped up about it.
</blockquote>
Yay, phase 2 is coming, but only 50 more people will be let in.  = (  But on the plus side, that means Phase 3 is getting closer.<br><br>
